      <title>大提顿国家公园，自我攻击的胡椒喷雾击退了一只攻击灰熊</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/22/g-s1-40/self-inflicted-hit-of-pepper-spray-drives-off-an-attacking-grizzly-in-grand-teton-national-park</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在信号山袭击一名徒步旅行者时，灰熊咬了这名男子的驱熊剂罐并逃跑了。这名马萨诸塞州男子在被咬时假装死亡，最终逃到了安全地带。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2024/05/22/g-s1-40/self-inflicted-hit-of-pepper-spray-drives-off-an-attacking-grizzly-in-grand-teton-national-park</guid>
